    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You cover your hand with earth release chakra before delivering a single palm strike in the center of your opponent's mass. Make a melee ninjutsu attack against a target you can see within range. On a hit, the target takes 4d4 + your ninjutsu ability modifier earth damage and must make a Strength saving throw, being knocked back 15 feet on a failed save.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above <br />D-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the damage by 2d4.</p>",
